    (h.fullRowRank_stackedFullColumnRank_iff_s_l22_diag_ne_zero).1
      ⟨hB, hstack⟩⟩

/-- Higham, 2nd ed., Chapter 20, Theorem 20.9, sentence after (20.28):
    source full row rank of `B` and full column rank of `[A; B]` construct
